      "content": "wait r u saying that religious freedom is actually more important than everyone being treated equally under the law though? cuz if some groups get special rules just because of their religion, doesn't that basically destroy the whole point of a secular democracy? it feels like you're siding with the idea that religious rights should trump equality.",
